{"tid":372161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求將8月23日訂為澳殤日","createTime":"2017-08-24T06:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:43:16.000Z","uid":108894,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bff9d50aef15c38c5d5d550acd3324f21814eb2","tid":372161,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"8月23日，澳門受天鴿吹襲，錄得史上最強風速，全市嚴重水浸，斷水斷電，係天災，更係人禍，除左目睹大自然嘅威力之外，更突顯澳門政府同氣象局嘅無能同闊佬懶理。如果唔係呢班撚樣無準備好應變方案，預測失準同無及時預警颱風直襲，澳門而家根本唔會死傷慘重，滿目瘡痍，而且水電都未完全恢復！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此，本人認為應該將23/8定為澳殤日，除左要記得天災嘅慘痛之外，仲要記得政府同氣象局嘅惡劣處事作風！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=唔需要"},{"pid":"10b1b65b2eb512ad0894356d9669ec39ba603917","tid":372161,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"國殤日"},{"pid":"3bdfe4d4ff742550b01f33a3510a75d0b1835cab","tid":372161,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"d2d839c801407ce49564c32336974febe774e7bd","tid":372161,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"有冇假放先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbaeff1a910910df8d3e0beb3d48ad250c15d2d","tid":372161,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbb4865f4ee16e56ea9d7795d27dc7289969b9b9","tid":372161,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"死得幾個人就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"a4884a452eb01c6492bc01e94d9a44cf2e6befd8","tid":372161,"uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2010年8月23號<br />\n你唔記得啦咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"h